          <actionDate>2017-05-04</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Highway Restoration Act of 201</strong><b>7</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide for a phaseout of the Mass Transit Account by the end of FY2021. Beginning in FY2022, no funds would be transferred to the account from the Highway Trust Fund. </p>]]></text>
